    "causal_summary": "After the executor purge in phases 001-003, \"Gemini\" still existed in the repo in two separate roles that phase 003 explicitly deferred: as a host runtime (the `hooks/gemini/` subsystems in system-spec-kit and system-skill-advisor, the `gemini-cli` member of every `RuntimeId` union and its detection logic, runtime fixtures, cross-runtime fallback, hook re-export parity, and the `GEMINI.md` root-doc convention) and as a model (`gemini-flash` in the deep-loop fallback router, the sk-prompt small-model budgets and profiles, and the cli-devin quota-fallback docs)",
